title: Live coverage: SpaceX to launch 450th Falcon rocket on Starlink 12-14 mission
summary: The flight will include 21 Starlink V2 Mini satellites, of which 13 have Direct to Cell capabilities. Liftoff from pad 40 at Cape Canaveral Space Force Station is set for 6:40 a.m. EST (1140 UTC).
